trans-unit.source: Represents a ribbon toolbar that is always visible in the window frame to provide access to common commands.
trans-unit.target: Representerer en båndet verktøylinje er alltid synlig i vindusrammen å gi tilgang til vanlige kommandoer.

trans-unit.source: You add a RibbonQuickAccessToolBar to a <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.Ribbon> control by specifying it as the content of the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.Ribbon.QuickAccessToolBar%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property using XAML [Property Element Syntax](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: Du legger til en RibbonQuickAccessToolBar til en <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.Ribbon>kontroll ved å angi den som innholdet i den <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.Ribbon.QuickAccessToolBar%2A?displayProperty=fullName>egenskapen ved hjelp av XAML [syntaks i Element egenskapen](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.Ribbon.QuickAccessToolBar%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.Ribbon>

trans-unit.source: ``` <ribbon:Ribbon> <ribbon:Ribbon.QuickAccessToolBar> <ribbon:RibbonQuickAccessToolBar /> </ribbon:Ribbon.QuickAccessToolBar> ... </ribbon:Ribbon> ``` The following list shows the typical placement of the RibbonQuickAccessToolBar in the hierarchy of ribbon elements.
trans-unit.target: ``` <ribbon:Ribbon> <ribbon:Ribbon.QuickAccessToolBar> <ribbon:RibbonQuickAccessToolBar /> </ribbon:Ribbon.QuickAccessToolBar> ... </ribbon:Ribbon> ```Følgende liste viser vanlige plasseringen av RibbonQuickAccessToolBar i hierarkiet båndet elementer.
